Enum Bitboard.Square

  • Object
    • Enum<Bitboard.Square>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Bitboard.Square>

    Bitboard

    public static enum Bitboard.Square
extends Enum<Bitboard.Square>
    An enum type for the 64 squares of the chess board. Each constant has a field that contains a long with only the bitboard on the respective square's index set.
    Author:
    Viktor
